-- ChTPZ Seeks 30 Billion-Ruble State Guarantee, Kommersant Reports
-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 2012-06-05T04:43:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/chtpz-seeks-30-billion-ruble-state-guarantee-kommersant-reports.html
ChTPZ Group, a Russian pipemaker,
requested a 30 billion-ruble ($897 million) state guarantee to
avoid a default,  Kommersant  reported, citing principal owner
Andrey Komarov.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran in Moscow at 
